Gam is library for Game Creator & Deigital Signage Developer

### Dependencies : Qt(ver 4.7), Box2D, OpenCV, OpenNI, NITE ####
$ git clone git@github.com:goccy/gam.git
$ cd gam

(1) Please install Box2D library
$ cd lib/Box2D
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../
$ make && make install

(2) Please install Qt4 library
/* This library needs QtOpenGL.*/

(3) Please install OpenCV & OpenNI

(4) Please install NITE
/* If your os is MacOSX */
$ cd lib/NITE
$ sudo ./install.sh /* copied to /usr/include/nite & /usr/lib/libXnV~.dylib */

(5) Building & Install
$ cd gam
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../
$ make
$ make install
==> copied to /usr/local/lib/libgam.{dylib, so, dll} & /usr/local/include/gam.hpp & /usr/local/bin/gamake

### Hello Gam Application
$ cd sample/physics
$ gamake /* generates Makefile */
$ make
$ open physics.app or ./physics.exe
